title: Wireless Wi-Fi HD Video Smart Bird Feeder Bird House with Camera and Solar Panel
item_description:
Wireless Wi-Fi HD Video Smart Bird Feeder Bird House with Camera and Solar Panel
Smart Bird Feeder with Camera - Wireless Outdoor Bird Watching with AI Recognition, Solar Powered Wild Bird Watching Gifts for Outside Hanging, Auto Image & Video Capture
Bird Watching in Real Time on Your Phone: Bird watching no longer requires binoculars! ERAMONG smart outdoor bird feeder with camera automatically captures and records video of all incoming birds, and you can receive real-time notifications of bird visits through your phone's app. This innovative smart bird feeder with camera brings you closer to birds and closer to nature.
1080P HD Camera & Color Night Vision: This smart bird watching camera feeder is equipped with an advanced AI recognition technology system capable of identifying over 11,000+ bird species. This feature enables you to effortlessly learn about the diverse array of birds that visit the feeder. Additionally, the 1080P high-resolution outdoor camera ensures optimal image and video capture, even in low-light conditions or at night.
A Beautiful Home for Backyard Birds: This camera bird feeder comes with a large 1.8L capacity bird feeder so you don't have to refill your bird food as often.The IP65 waterproof rating and sturdy stand make it a solid home for birds. These bird-friendly features will appeal to a variety of birds. Our wireless outdoor camera bird feeder has a wider and sturdier construction, allowing you to add different add-ons to customise your feeding station.
Solar Powered & Stable Connection: Equipped with a flexible and adjustable solar panel, this bird feeder ensures continuous operation through its solar-powered design and built-in 5000mAh rechargeable battery. The bird feeder camera also features a 5dB antenna, supporting a stable 2.4GHz Wi-Fi connection (not compatible with 5GHz networks). With these features, you'll never have to worry about missing any bird moments.
Ideal Gift For Your Families & Multi-User Share: Still on the hunt for the perfect gifts for your family? The smart bird feeder is a good choice. The smart bird feeder with camera stores bird videos and pictures in the cloud for free for up to 30 days, and you can extend the storage time with a subscription or by storing them on a TF card (not included). You can share beautiful moments with children and elderly anytime, anywhere.
Product information
Brand ERAMONG
Target Species Birds
Recommended Uses For Product Bird Watching
Material ABS Plastic & Acrylic
Special Feature Solar Panel, Night Vision Full Color, Auto Picture and Video Capture, Weatherproof, DIY Perch
Mounting Type Freestanding, Wall Mount, Tree Mount, Pole Mount
Product Dimensions 9.1"L x 10.8"W x 13.1"H
Power Source Solar Powered
Included Components Bird Feeder, Roof, Perch, Perch Screw, Tripod Adapter, Mounting Bracket, Quick Guide, Type C Charger Cable, Drilling Template, Hose Clip, Black Strap, Mounting Screws x 3, Anchors x 3, Ejector Pin, Solar Panel
Capacity 1.8 Liters
Theme Garden
Color Orange
Item Weight 5.52 pounds
Manufacturer ERAMONG
Country of Origin China
Item model number AI bird feeder
Batteries 2 Lithium Ion batteries required. (included)
